 /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"54eb7b35eb2bbdcd0032f8c1f3699b420a354485","tid":787262,"uid":27785,"like":22,"dislike":2,"score":20,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-21T06:05:59.000Z","msg":"獌而家有邊個有佢係邊路既突破能力<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 上季中本身踢得好好地又俾摩狗雪<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 幾勁都踢唔起啦屌"},{"pid":"466f242655482e8aeec964ab4a142285e60a4246","tid":787262,"uid":28435,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-21T06:08:06.000Z","msg":"打fifa勁"},{"pid":"cb32048156dd023cd505eafc86b2494d702598de","tid":787262,"uid":67225,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"54eb7b35eb2bbdcd0032f8c1f3699b420a354485","tid":787262,"uid":27785,"like":22,"dislike":2,"score":20,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-21T06:05:59.000Z","msg":"獌而家有邊個有佢係邊路既突破能力<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 上季中本身踢得好好地又俾摩狗雪<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 幾勁都踢唔起啦屌"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-21T07:52:40.000Z","msg":"佢有突破能力但都係一般水平以下（而家嚟講）"},{"pid":"2d9cb84b15b4fed3547c51058124a4f8e77afc30","tid":787262,"uid":19126,"like":27,"dislike":4,"score":23,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-21T08:11:07.000Z","msg":"其實個人能力冇問題，係摩狗戰術太過時，馬仔本身打正前都幾好，但又唔太俾機會佢，推左佢去打翼但又唔教佢打翼既意識、臨場可以點做，所以好迷失，當年係v92手下佢好清楚自己就係要入波，所以係禁區其實佢仲勁過lkk、華豬福，起碼意識好，執雞又冷靜，放佢打翼好浪費<br />\n<br />\n打翼方面佢好迷失，又冇人教，搞到慣性扣大位鳩射<br />\n<br />\n猶記得當年楊格初到曼聯都係咁，開季作客西布朗係咁扣大位俾人mark死，下半場費sir提醒佢要落底，結果俾佢落底出波，對面og一球贏左<br />\n<br />\n呢個就係領隊功力既分野<br />\n<br />\n當年費sir都會兩隻翼調下位，或者指個中場過去幫手組織下，又有長短傳，對手好難防，依家摩狗一味短傳組織，長傳就一定唔係分邊，係後半場直接鳩斬俾前鋒<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n以前費sir分邊就算唔到，好多時都有個界外球，變左已經可以壓前隊波做組織，依家摩狗組織兩下就係中路斷左，所以曼聯一直贏和輸都冇氣勢，根本就猜唔到幾腳波就失<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f5c8257d3bc4dbc7fb1e45684bda0d5e8966e0d7","tid":787262,"uid":45108,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"332154c9cb5ab70fe1b88b2bb02cc4733523c552","tid":787262,"uid":54945,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-21T06:01:47.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>希望你係認真，我都認真下<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n初加盟個季的確係幾搶眼<br />\n以一個法甲初出道計係幾好波<br />\n之後兩年完全冇進步過<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">同期既福仔雖然叫點錯能力<br />\n多左罰波同出波呢2範但起碼有進步睇到</span><br />\n加上有變速又可以踢前個波鬥快跑<br />\n馬斯亞就淨係識妹<br />\n妹唔緊要，成功率仲低過普巴<br />\n成日諗住妹入中間射<br />\n係就學下世三咁踢等對家冇腳影捉啦<br />\n<br />\n係daddy唔識教定佢自己能力有限真係唔知<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-21T08:21:03.000Z","msg":"福有進步<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"36bf32c5b919b962415c197b1a46a1316472237c","tid":787262,"uid":5649,"like":13,"dislike":0,"score":13,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-21T08:23:17.000Z","msg":"認真佢比哥狗教變能左世4"},{"pid":"9b54efbadce6f09161c7ccea21a43dcd66295581","tid":787262,"uid":78574,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-21T08:26:49.000Z","msg":"摩狗教到攻擊球員有進步既例子應該得好少數<img src=\