16:38:06.000Z","msg":"以佢當年咁後生，對利記入個咁嘅波<br />\n好公道講係值得捧到上天<br />\n加上佢個人能力真心唔差<br />\n個問題係遇著摩連奴<br />\n福仔同佢喺摩狗手上完全冇進步過<br />\n愈踢愈沉真係好正常<br />\n<br />\n時也命也，年中幾多妖人橫空出世<br />\n又有幾多個最後真係成材？<br />\n所以唔洗太介懷"},{"pid":"f4b5b10f2fb7acedd6b43d81a97da4a7f6c2a528","tid":787262,"uid":67225,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"9d61828fe05600fc679f5ce2f73b0e4a12b4c3bc","tid":787262,"uid":55981,"like":3,"dislike":3,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-21T16:04:03.000Z","msg":"韋碧克都勁過佢<br />\n起碼爆得起又有鬥心"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-21T16:39:21.000Z","msg":"我地成隊無一個肯爆<br />\nLin果隻叫推個波落人地到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e5faf9f4b6dd6b4ddd6f63a39006293f73181b3e","tid":787262,"uid":133756,"like":5,"dislike":1,"score":4,"quote":{"pid":"f771641f53bd943ceb85be44c1099aab8db24067","tid":787262,"uid":143965,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-21T15:57:36.000Z","msg":"似心態問題喎 唔憂踢咁撚樣 個款似等走"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-08-21T16:56:48.000Z","msg":"生個仔都罰半個月糧<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n點會有心踢"},{"pid":"a82f52926dbdf1a1d1eadb95b123c0b86d795544","tid":787262,"uid":59400,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"e5faf9f4b6dd6b4ddd6f63a39006293f73181b3e","tid":787262,"uid":133756,"like":5,"dislike":1,"score":4,"quote":{"pid":"f771641f53bd943ceb85be44c1099aab8db24067","tid":787262,"uid":143965,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-21T15:57:36.000Z","msg":"似心態問題喎 唔憂踢咁撚樣 個款似等走"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-08-21T16:56:48.000Z","msg":"生個仔都罰半個月糧<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n點會有心踢"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-21T18:06:33.000Z","msg":"同大衛施華個待遇差幾遠<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4d7d2899a1abd1436cba6f8d57354cde895517c9","tid":787262,"uid":760,"like":0,"dislike":11,"score":-11,"quote":{"pid":